reviewText: Purchased this item as a gift for someone else.
nice too see these guys outside the wheelhouse and relaxing a bit.
DC is never NOT awesome, and this DVD doesn't disappoint! The ONLY thing I'd wish is for it to be a longer show. And Phil is there-enough said.
my daughter loves the deadliest catch show and this dvd was perfect! i would recommend it if you are an ardent fan of the show.
